〈'''大家都不爽我'''〉<ref>{{cite AV media |title=老菸槍雙人組 The Chainsmokers / 大家都不爽我 Everybody Hates Me (HD中字MV) |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2VHTKX9dlrg |language=zh |deadurl=no |date=2018-05-02 |accessdate=2021-01-18 |publisher=台灣索尼音樂 Sony Music Taiwan YouTube 頻道 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20210118080229/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2VHTKX9dlrg |archivedate=2021-01-18 }}</ref>（{{lang-en|"Everybody Hates Me"}}）是美国[[唱片骑师|DJ]][[烟鬼组合|烟鬼组合]]演唱的单曲。歌曲由烟鬼组合和{{tsl|en|Shaun Frank|肖恩·弗兰克}}制作，{{tsl|en|Emily Warren|埃米莉·沃伦}}和安德鲁·塔格特作词，安德鲁·塔格特作曲。〈大家都不爽我〉为烟鬼组合第二张[[录音室专辑|录音室专辑]]《[[厌世男孩_(专辑)|厌世男孩]]》的第三首单曲，并于2018年3月16日经{{tsl|en|Disruptor Records|破坏者唱片}}和[[哥伦比亚唱片|哥伦比亚唱片]]发行。歌曲的官方音乐视频获[[2018年MTV音乐录影带大奖|2018年MTV音乐录影带大奖]]最佳舞曲奖提名<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://variety.com/2018/music/news/cardi-b-beyonce-jay-z-lead-2018-mtv-vma-video-music-awards-nominations-1202874001/|title=Cardi B, Beyonce, Jay-Z Lead 2018 MTV VMA Nominations|author=Variety Staff|date=2018-07-16|work=Variety|access-date=2018-07-16|archive-date=2018-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180716224135/https://variety.com/2018/music/news/cardi-b-beyonce-jay-z-lead-2018-mtv-vma-video-music-awards-nominations-1202874001/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景==
2018年2月11日，烟鬼组合在[[布拉格|布拉格]]的现场演出中首次演唱了〈大家都不爽我〉<ref>{{cite news|last=Bein|first=Kat|title=The Chainsmokers Perform Anthemic Unreleased Tune in Prague: Watch|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8099170/the-chainsmokers-new-song-video|accessdate=2018-03-16|work=Billboard|date=2018-02-12|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121043953/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8099170/the-chainsmokers-new-song-video|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Narozniak|first=Rachel|title=See The Chainsmokers perform an unreleased song in Prague [Watch]|url=http://www.dancingastronaut.com/2018/02/see-chainsmokers-perform-unreleased-song-prague-watch/|accessdate=2018-03-16|work={{tsl|en|Dancing Astronaut||Dancing Astronaut}}|date=2018-02-13|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128005733/https://dancingastronaut.com/2018/02/see-chainsmokers-perform-unreleased-song-prague-watch/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月13日，他们首次发布了歌曲预告片，片中包含了MV的一个镜头，视频中二人站在一辆着火的汽车前。第二天，〈大家都不爽我〉随封面图正式发行<ref>{{cite news|last=Bein|first=Kat|title=The Chainsmokers Announce New Single 'Everybody Hates Me' Coming Friday|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8242785/the-chainsmokers-new-music-teaser|accessdate=2018-03-16|work=Billboard|date=2018-03-13|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121001611/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8242785/the-chainsmokers-new-music-teaser|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Hulton|first=Anna|title=The Chainsmokers reveal details for their new single due to drop VERY soon|url=https://planetradio.co.uk/kiss/entertainment/music/the-chainsmokers-everybody-hates-me/|accessdate=2018-03-16|work={{tsl|en|Kiss (UK radio station)||Kiss}}|date=2018-03-15|archive-date=2019-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808091000/https://planetradio.co.uk/kiss/entertainment/music/the-chainsmokers-everybody-hates-me/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==作曲==
据[[CBS电台|CBS电台]]的乔恩·威德合恩（Jon Wiederhorn）报道，“〈大家都不爽我〉属中速并带有嘻哈风格的歌曲，内容与沮丧和幻想破灭相关”<ref name="CBS">{{cite news|last=Wiederhorn|first=Jon|title=The Chainsmokers Drop New Song 'Everybody Hates Me': Listen|url=http://news.radio.com/2018/03/16/the-chainsmokers-everybody-hates-me/|accessdate=2018-03-16|work=CBS Radio|date=2018-03-16|archive-date=2018-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180317035805/http://news.radio.com/2018/03/16/the-chainsmokers-everybody-hates-me/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌词方面，歌曲讨论了自我批评和成名同时并存的情况<ref>{{cite news|title=LISTEN: The Chainsmokers Debut 'Everybody Hates Me'|url=http://www.iheartradio.ca/chum-fm/music-news/listen-the-chainsmokers-debut-everybody-hates-me-1.3692613|accessdate=2018-03-16|work=[[iHeartRadio|iHeartRadio]]|date=2018-03-16|archive-date=2018-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180317102332/http://www.iheartradio.ca/chum-fm/music-news/listen-the-chainsmokers-debut-everybody-hates-me-1.3692613|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==评价==
{{tsl|en|MTV News|MTV新闻}}的帕特里克·霍斯肯（Patrick Hosken）认为〈大家都不爽我〉是“德鲁·塔格特放弃了演唱，以[[德雷克_(歌手)|德雷克]]的方式回顾了内心的不安全感”，他写道塔格特的声音“听上去最接近于他从小崇拜乐队的歌曲中典型emo风格的哀鸣，像是[[眨眼182|眨眼182]]和[[迪斯科瘪三|迪斯科瘪三]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Hosken|first=Patrick|title=Everybody Hates The Chainsmokers On Gloomy New Song|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/3069782/the-chainsmokers-everybody-hates-me/|accessdate=2018-03-16|work=MTV News|date=2018-03-16|archive-date=2020-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103223901/http://www.mtv.com/news/3069782/the-chainsmokers-everybody-hates-me/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。CBS电台的乔恩·威德合恩认为这首歌“是烟鬼组合将朗朗上口、重节奏的EDM与流行音乐融合的又一个例子”<ref name="CBS"/>。[[Vice_(杂志)|Noisey]]的劳伦·奥尼尔（Lauren O'Neill）“通过Chainsmokers-Ness”订购了歌词，并称〈大家都不爽我〉为“一首非常烟鬼组合的歌曲”<ref>{{cite news|last=O'Neill|first=Lauren|title=Ordering The Chainsmokers "Everybody Hates Me" Lyrics by Chainsmokers-Ness|url=https://noisey.vice.com/en_uk/article/43bgnw/chainsmokers-everybody-hates-me-lyrics-ranked-by-chainsmokers-ness|accessdate=2018-03-16|work=Noisey|date=2018-03-16|archive-date=2019-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421195117/https://noisey.vice.com/en_uk/article/43bgnw/chainsmokers-everybody-hates-me-lyrics-ranked-by-chainsmokers-ness|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|Uproxx}}》的德里克·罗西尼奥尔（Derrick Rossignol）认为这首歌是“我们期待从烟鬼组合那里得到的EDM流行歌曲类型”以及“二人更具个人风格的歌曲之一”<ref>{{cite news|last=Rossignol|first=Derrick|title=The Chainsmokers Are Tired Of Being The Villains On Their New Single 'Everybody Hates Me'|url=https://uproxx.com/music/chainsmokers-everybody-hates-me-new-song/|accessdate=2018-03-17|work=Uproxx|date=2018-03-16|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929150603/https://uproxx.com/music/chainsmokers-everybody-hates-me-new-song/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[Spin_(杂志)|Spin]]》的安迪·库什（Andy Cush）写道：“〈大家都不爽我〉有一个可取之处：这是一首可与〈[[玫瑰朵朵|玫瑰朵朵]]〉相媲美的EDM音乐，传达的正是他们于此前对〈[[厌世男孩_(烟鬼组合歌曲)|厌世男孩]]〉和〈[[你欠我的|你欠我的]]〉的抱怨中刻意隐瞒的合成器糖衣炮弹式的满足感。”<ref>{{cite news|last=Cush|first=Andy|title=The Chainsmokers Have a Moment of Clarity|url=https://www.spin.com/2018/03/the-chainsmokers-everybody-hates-me-stream/|accessdate=2018-03-17|work=Spin|date=2018-03-16|archive-date=2020-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128174505/https://www.spin.com/2018/03/the-chainsmokers-everybody-hates-me-stream/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

